    "abstract": "<jats:title>ABSTRACT</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>This study is a retrospective cohort of 122 adult patients with SARS-CoV-2 diagnosed and managed at two medium-sized, tertiary private Hospitals. The analysis includes demographic and socio-economic information, symptoms, comorbidities, laboratory test results, therapeutic management, clinical outcomes and complications.</jats:p>",
